```
## Quick Review Summary

### 🧑‍💻 Developer
🔴 [Critical issue]
🟡 [Suggestion]
✅ [Good pattern observed]

### 🎨 UX
🔴 [Accessibility issue]
🟡 [UX improvement]

### 🧪 QE
🟡 [Untested edge case]
🟢 [Minor test suggestion]

### 🔒 Security
✅ [Security looks good]

### 🌐 i18n Compliance
🔴 [Untranslated string / wrong TFunction type]
✅ [All strings properly translated]

### 📏 Code Standards
🟡 [File structure / naming issue]
✅ [Standards followed]
```

